<node CREATED="1669259185890" ID="ID_1961404847" MODIFIED="1669378612032" TEXT="&lt;enable if played in south america&gt; I want to play &quot;AK47&quot;!">
<node CREATED="1669378505088" ID="ID_1033692646" MODIFIED="1669378653784" TEXT="Spike: Why do I get the feeling, that if i refuse you&apos;ll propose a trading card game? Fine, I&apos;m not a big fan of this savage game, but as I&apos;m scared of what you&apos;ll offer instead, I&apos;ll concede if you really want to play it.">
<node CREATED="1669378656462" ID="ID_1641949164" MODIFIED="1670456794539" TEXT="Yes, let&apos;s go!">
