<node CREATED="1669259551938" ID="ID_1479981027" MODIFIED="1669259593890" TEXT="&lt;enable if played in Japan&gt; I really prefer &quot;Poor man&apos;s MahJongg&quot;">
<node CREATED="1669341967938" ID="ID_961285423" MODIFIED="1669342159077" TEXT="Spike: That trash, played by pre-historic japanese farmers and peasants? I did not take you for a degenerate, but it seems like I have overestimated your cultural tastes. Fortunately for me, we don&apos;t have the personell to play this game. We don&apos;t have a west and east wind after all... Let&apos;s play something else!">
